      <div xml:id="gbs333-h62772"> <!-- l3d26prae -->
        <head xml:id="gbs333-h62772-Hd1e100">Praeambulum</head>
        <p xml:id="gbs333-h62772-d1e102">
          <lb ed="#B" n="20"/>DISTINCTIO XXVI. 
          <lb ed="#B" n="21"/>De spe. 
          <lb ed="#B" n="22"/>ETERMINATO 
          <lb ed="#B" n="23"/>de fide prima uirtute 
          <lb ed="#B" n="24"/>theologicali in. iii. 
          pr<lb ed="#B" n="25" break="no"/>cedentibus 
          distinctio<lb ed="#B" n="26" break="no"/>nibus: consequenter 
          <lb ed="#B" n="27"/>in hac distinct. xxvi. 
          <lb ed="#B" n="28"/>magister agit de 
          uir<lb ed="#B" n="29" break="no"/>tutespei, quae est secunda uirtus 
          theologi<lb ed="#B" n="30" break="no"/>ca: cuius sententia in sequentibus 
          con<lb ed="#B" n="31" break="no"/>clusionibus summarie continetur.
        </p>
        <p xml:id="gbs333-h62772-d1e131">
          ¶ 
          Pri<lb ed="#B" n="32" break="no"/>ma conclusio. Spes est certa expectatio  
          <lb ed="#B" n="33"/>suturae beatitudinis ueniens ex dei 
          gra<lb ed="#B" n="34" break="no"/>tia, &amp; praecedentibus meritis.
        </p>
        <p xml:id="gbs333-h62772-d1e140">
          ¶ Secunda 
          <lb ed="#B" n="35"/>conclusio. Fides, &amp; spes in eo, quod sunt non 
          <lb ed="#B" n="36"/>apparentium conueniunt: sed quia fides 
          <lb ed="#B" n="37"/>est de bonis, &amp; malis praeteritis 
          praesen<lb ed="#B" n="38" break="no"/>tibus, &amp; futuris: spes tantum de bonis 
          fu<lb ed="#B" n="39" break="no"/>turis: sicut uocabulo, ita differentia 
          ra<lb ed="#B" n="40" break="no"/>tionali differunt.
        </p>
        <p xml:id="gbs333-h62772-d1e157">
          ¶ Tertia conclusio. In 
          <lb ed="#B" n="41"/>christo sicut in beatis: nec fidei, 
          neque<lb ed="#B" n="42" break="no"/>spei uirtus fuit: quamuis quaedam 
          spera<lb ed="#B" n="43" break="no"/>uit, &amp; credidit. In quo dicto magistri, 
          <lb ed="#B" n="44"/>uerbum credidit large accipitur: 
          <lb ed="#B" n="45"/>pro firmiter assentire uero 
          <lb ed="#B" n="46"/>prout includit 
          ui<lb ed="#B" n="47" break="no"/>sionem.
        </p>
      </div>
